INSERT INTO `system_log` VALUES ('773', '127.0.0.1', 'blog/article/edit', 'admin', 'blog/article/edit', '{\"id\":\"8\",\"title\":\"关于博主\",\"isfabu\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<h3 style=\\\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; color: rgb(71, 115, 177); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;, Georgia; line-height: 1.1; font-size: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); transition: all 0.5s; white-space: normal;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/h3>\\n\\n<p class=\\\"code_h3\\\" style=\\\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\\\">About Blog<\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=\\\"code_pt_biaoti\\\" style=\\\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 10px 15px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-width: 1px 1px 1px 3px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(227, 227, 227) rgb(227, 227, 227) rgb(227, 227, 227) rgb(61, 171, 206); border-image: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;, Georgia; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\\\">这博客是在2018年01月10日创建的，一个非商业化、无盈利性质的个人博客。<\\/p>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; color: rgb(71, 115, 177); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;, Georgia; line-height: 1.1; font-size: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); transition: all 0.5s; white-space: normal;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/h3>\\n\\n<p class=\\\"code_h3\\\" style=\\\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\\\">About Me<\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=\\\"code_pt_biaoti\\\" style=\\\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 10px 15px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-width: 1px 1px 1px 3px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(227, 227, 227) rgb(227, 227, 227) rgb(227, 227, 227) rgb(61, 171, 206); border-image: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;, Georgia; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\\\"><span style=\\\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); text-indent: 0em;\\\">90后，工作两年。<br \\/>\\n一直对计算机很感兴趣，自学，然后走入这一行。<br \\/>\\n<br \\/>\\n工作php，这期间学会前端技术，ionic，android，python，除了工作中项目，自己大大小小写写小东西，就是好玩，从没想过要去盈利什么的，不管上不上班，每天要写个两小时代码，似乎已经变成了习惯，不然总觉得少做了什么，晚上睡不着<br \\/>\\n<br \\/>\\n两年工作时间，一晃而过，回首过往，才发现不知道有什么可回忆的，是的啊，总要做点什么，来留住昨天，博客是开始，做一件事，专注，坚持下去，然后等待时间的回报。。。<\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; color: rgb(71, 115, 177); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;, Georgia; line-height: 1.1; font-size: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); transition: all 0.5s; white-space: normal;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/h3>\\n\\n<p class=\\\"code_h3\\\" style=\\\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\\\">About Copyright<\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=\\\"code_pt_biaoti\\\" style=\\\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 10px 15px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-width: 1px 1px 1px 3px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(227, 227, 227) rgb(227, 227, 227) rgb(227, 227, 227) rgb(61, 171, 206); border-image: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;, Georgia; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\\\">文章有来自网络，但一定是我认为有价值的，不会去写爬虫无脑顺，转载必标明作者和来源，倘若侵犯您的版权，告知后立马删除。同样，秉着网络共享的精神，希望大家在我这里转载文章时候也能留下我的署名和链接。<\\/p>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; color: rgb(71, 115, 177); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;, Georgia; line-height: 1.1; font-size: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); transition: all 0.5s; white-space: normal;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/h3>\\n\\n<p class=\\\"code_h3\\\" style=\\\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\\\">About Content<\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=\\\"code_pt_biaoti\\\" style=\\\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 10px 15px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-width: 1px 1px 1px 3px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(227, 227, 227) rgb(227, 227, 227) rgb(227, 227, 227) rgb(61, 171, 206); border-image: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;, Georgia; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\\\">内容方面只要是技术分享，有一些科技资讯，都是跟技术相关的，主要是自己亲手或亲身经历过的技术文摘和网络上一些有趣的东西。因为兴趣爱好才接触的网站，然后顺其自然的想做一个个人博客，最后这博客就诞生了。<\\/p>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin: 10px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; color: rgb(71, 115, 177); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;, Georgia; line-height: 1.1; font-size: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); transition: all 0.5s; white-space: normal;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/h3>\\n\\n<p class=\\\"code_h3\\\" style=\\\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\\\">Contact Me<\\/p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;, Georgia; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<p class=\\\"code_blue\\\" style=\\\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 22px 15px 15px 70px; border: 1px solid rgb(138, 204, 255); background: url(&quot;image\\/code_blue.png&quot;) 20px 20px no-repeat rgb(195, 229, 255); color: rgb(13, 112, 187); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, &quot;Arial Narrow&quot;, Georgia; white-space: normal;\\\">QQ：1922884595<br \\/>\\n<span style=\\\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0); text-indent: 0em;\\\">没事别加..不和陌生人闲聊..<br \\/>\\nEmail：1922884595@qq.com&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\",\"tags\":\"\",\"category\":\"14\",\"thumb\":\"\\/static\\/upload\\/0e4516d393ecec13\\/03661aa0b1d7e7c8.jpg\",\"laiyuan\":\"\"}', '', '2019-01-06 16:32:41');
INSERT INTO `system_log` VALUES ('774', '127.0.0.1', 'blog/article/edit', 'admin', 'blog/article/edit', '{\"id\":\"9\",\"title\":\"最近很火的跳一跳，python3，最简单版本\",\"isfabu\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/ss1.baidu.com\\/6ONXsjip0QIZ8tyhnq\\/it\\/u=901384762,3075970337&amp;fm=55&amp;s=D4A0BF576DC3CA57580D2DFE0300C02A&amp;w=320&amp;h=160&amp;img.JPG\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>最简单跳一跳，手动画点，精准操作自动化<\\/p>\\n\\n<pre style=\\\"background-color:#272822;color:#f8f8f2;font-family:\'Consolas\';font-size:15.6pt;\\\">\\n<span style=\\\"font-size: 18px;\\\">import&nbsp;matplotlib.pyplot&nbsp;as&nbsp;plt\\nimport&nbsp;os\\nimport&nbsp;numpy&nbsp;as&nbsp;np\\nfrom&nbsp;PIL&nbsp;import&nbsp;Image\\n\\nfig&nbsp;=&nbsp;plt.figure()\\ncor&nbsp;=&nbsp;[]\\nclick_count&nbsp;=&nbsp;0\\ndierci=False\\nlastcor=()\\npos=()\\n\\ndef&nbsp;jump(distance):\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;press_time&nbsp;=&nbsp;distance&nbsp;*&nbsp;1.35\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;press_time&nbsp;=&nbsp;int(press_time)\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cmd&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;adb&nbsp;shell&nbsp;input&nbsp;swipe&nbsp;320&nbsp;410&nbsp;320&nbsp;410&nbsp;&#39;&nbsp;+&nbsp;str(press_time)\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;print(cmd)\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;os.system(cmd)\\n\\ndef&nbsp;pull_screenshot():\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;os.system(&#39;adb&nbsp;shell&nbsp;screencap&nbsp;-p&nbsp;\\/sdcard\\/autojump.png&#39;)\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;os.system(&#39;adb&nbsp;pull&nbsp;\\/sdcard\\/autojump.png&nbsp;E:\\/python\\/first\\/screenshot\\/screenshot.png&#39;)\\n\\ndef&nbsp;openImg():\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;pull_screenshot()\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;img&nbsp;=&nbsp;np.array(Image.open(&#39;E:\\/python\\/first\\/screenshot\\/screenshot.png&#39;))\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;im&nbsp;=&nbsp;plt.imshow(img,&nbsp;animated=True)\\n\\ndef&nbsp;on_click2(i2x,i2y):\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;global&nbsp;lastcor\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ix=lastcor[0]\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;iy=lastcor[1]\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;distance&nbsp;=&nbsp;(i2x&nbsp;-&nbsp;ix)**2&nbsp;+&nbsp;(i2y&nbsp;-&nbsp;iy)**2\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;distance&nbsp;=&nbsp;distance&nbsp;**&nbsp;0.5\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;print(&#39;distance&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;,&nbsp;distance)\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;plt.close()\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;jump(distance)\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;lastcor=(i2x,i2y)\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;rebot()\\n\\ndef&nbsp;on_click1(ix,iy,i2x,i2y):\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;global&nbsp;lastcor\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;global&nbsp;dierci\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;distance&nbsp;=&nbsp;(i2x&nbsp;-&nbsp;ix)**2&nbsp;+&nbsp;(i2y&nbsp;-&nbsp;iy)**2\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;distance&nbsp;=&nbsp;distance&nbsp;**&nbsp;0.5\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;print(&#39;distance&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;,&nbsp;distance)\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;plt.close()\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;jump(distance)\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;lastcor=(i2x,i2y)\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;rebot()\\n\\ndef&nbsp;rebot():\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;global&nbsp;dierci\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;pull_screenshot();\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;openImg();\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if&nbsp;dierci&nbsp;is&nbsp;True:\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;pos=plt.ginput(1)\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;on_click2(pos[0][0],pos[0][1])\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;else:\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;pos=plt.ginput(2)\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;on_click1(pos[0][0],pos[0][1],pos[1][0],pos[1][1])\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;plt.show()\\n\\nrebot();<\\/span>\\n<\\/pre>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\",\"tags\":\"\",\"category\":\"4\",\"thumb\":\"\\/static\\/plugs\\/uploader\\/theme\\/image.png\",\"laiyuan\":\"\"}', '', '2019-01-06 16:32:50');
