INSERT INTO `system_log` VALUES ('868', '127.0.0.1', 'blog/article/edit', 'admin', 'blog/article/edit', '{\"id\":\"45\",\"title\":\"游戏素材资源获取方法\",\"isfabu\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.7em; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 27.2px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">我们刚开始做游戏时大多数人都不能独立制作出想要的游戏资源，所以在没有商业用途的游戏里，我们可以用别人已经制作出来的游戏资源来山寨出一款自己的游戏，那么怎么获取这些游戏素材呢？<\\/p>\\n\\n<h2 style=\\\"margin: 0.8em 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 2.15em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">1.Cocos官方资源商店<\\/h2>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.7em; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 27.2px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/store.cocos.com\\/\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(12, 137, 207);\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">http:\\/\\/store.cocos.com\\/<\\/a>&nbsp;<br \\/>\\n<strong style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\\">虽然官方暂时不维护了，但里面的资源还是有很多的，而且种类多，还有一些源码可以学习，只需要注册一个Cocos开发者账号就可以了。Unity商店同理，但Unity大多数的资源都是要钱的。<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.7em; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 27.2px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<h2 style=\\\"white-space: normal; margin: 0.8em 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 2.15em; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">2.素材网站，有很多源码下载&nbsp;<\\/h2>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.7em; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 27.2px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\\"><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.6m5m.com\\\">http:\\/\\/www.6m5m.com<\\/a><\\/strong><\\/p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.7em; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 27.2px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">注册账号就可以下载了，有的资源需要积分<\\/p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.7em; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 27.2px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\\n<h2 style=\\\"margin: 0.8em 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 2.15em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">3.相关游戏素材分享网站<\\/h2>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.7em; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 27.2px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.2gei.com\\/\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(12, 137, 207);\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">http:\\/\\/www.2gei.com\\/<\\/a>&nbsp;<br \\/>\\n<strong style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\\">完全免费的，我只用过这个，其他网站可以去网上搜一下<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n\\n<h2 style=\\\"margin: 0.8em 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 2.15em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">4.（非常可耻的）用别人做好的游戏安装包<\\/h2>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.7em; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 27.2px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><strong style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\\">我们随便到进入一个应用商店，比如我们想做炸弹人这个游戏，我们就搜索炸弹人相关关键字，选择一个下载到电脑上，这个安装包的后缀名是.apk,我们把后缀名改为.zip,然后利用解压工具解压，里面就有你想要的资源了（一些大型的游戏会有格式加密，有些资源是拿不到的）<\\/strong><\\/p>\\n\\n<blockquote style=\\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.7em; line-height: 27.2px; padding: 15px 20px; border-left: 10px solid rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.0745098); background-color: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.0470588); border-radius: 0px 5px 5px 0px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; white-space: normal;\\\">\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1em; color: rgb(111, 111, 111); word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal;\\\">最后我还是要说一句，用别人的资源只能用来学习，不要用于任何商业用途，愿世界对每一个游戏开发者温柔以待。<\\/p>\\n<\\/blockquote>\\n\\n<h2 style=\\\"margin: 0.8em 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 2.15em; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">4.国外（如果你能看懂英语）<\\/h2>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.7em; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 27.2px; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: normal; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/opengameart.org\\/\\\" style=\\\"text-decoration: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(12, 137, 207);\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">http:\\/\\/opengameart.org\\/<\\/a><\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\",\"tags\":\"\",\"category\":\"20\",\"thumb\":\"\\/static\\/upload\\/ab0d49adff56e5fb\\/959ffcfba18f8f12.jpg\",\"laiyuan\":\"http:\\/\\/blog.csdn.net\\/potato47\\/article\\/details\\/51866057\"}', '', '2019-01-06 16:49:52');
