INSERT INTO `system_log` VALUES ('893', '127.0.0.1', 'blog/article/edit', 'admin', 'blog/article/edit', '{\"id\":\"56\",\"title\":\"thinkphp5+swoole实现异步邮件群发（SMTP方式）\",\"isfabu\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<h3 style=\\\"margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 3px 0px 3px 8px; font-size: 1.1em; border-left: 5px solid rgb(60, 140, 221); background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal;\\\">1、环境说明<\\/h3>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">阿里云centos7<br \\/>\\nthinkphp5.0.11<br \\/>\\nswoole2.0.8<\\/p>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\\"margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 3px 0px 3px 8px; font-size: 1.1em; border-left: 5px solid rgb(60, 140, 221); background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal;\\\">2、tp实现邮件发送<\\/h3>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">在项目下建立如下的文件目录：<br \\/>\\n<img alt=\\\"mail.png\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/blog.blueyian.top\\/usr\\/uploads\\/2017\\/10\\/792409954.png\\\" title=\\\"mail.png\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">其中SendMail.php是我们实际调用的发送邮件的文件。以下是主要代码：<\\/p>\\n\\n<pre style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0.6em; padding-bottom: 0.6em; position: relative; overflow: hidden; border-left: 5px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(93, 106, 106); white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; word-break: break-word; letter-spacing: 0.14px;\\\">\\nnamespace&nbsp;app\\\\library\\\\utils\\\\mail;\\nuse&nbsp;app\\\\library\\\\utils\\\\mail\\\\PhpMailer;\\nuse&nbsp;app\\\\library\\\\utils\\\\mail\\\\Smtp;\\nuse&nbsp;think\\\\Log;\\n\\nerror_reporting(E_STRICT);\\ndate_default_timezone_set(&#39;Asia\\/Shanghai&#39;);\\n\\nclass&nbsp;SendMail\\n{\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;static&nbsp;function&nbsp;postmail($to,$subject&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;&#39;,$body&nbsp;=&nbsp;&#39;&#39;){\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail&nbsp;=&nbsp;new&nbsp;PhpMailer();\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;CharSet&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&nbsp;config(&#39;mail.CharSet&#39;);\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;IsSMTP();\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;SMTPDebug&nbsp;&nbsp;=&nbsp;config(&#39;mail.SMTPDebug&#39;);\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;SMTPAuth&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&nbsp;config(&#39;mail.SMTPAuth&#39;);\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;SMTPSecure&nbsp;=&nbsp;config(&#39;mail.SMTPSecure&#39;);\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;Host&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&nbsp;config(&#39;mail.Host&#39;);\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;Port&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&nbsp;config(&#39;mail.Port&#39;);\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;Username&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&nbsp;config(&#39;mail.Username&#39;);\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;Password&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&nbsp;config(&#39;mail.Password&#39;);\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;SetFrom(config(&#39;mail.From&#39;),&nbsp;config(&#39;mail.Name&#39;));\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;Subject&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=&nbsp;$subject;\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;MsgHTML($body);\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$address&nbsp;=&nbsp;$to;\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$mail-&gt;AddAddress($address,&nbsp;&#39;&#39;);\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if(!$mail-&gt;Send())&nbsp;{\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Log::write(&#39;send&nbsp;to&nbsp;&#39;.$to.&#39;error&nbsp;info:&#39;.$mail-&gt;ErrorInfo);\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;false;\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;else&nbsp;{\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;true;\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\\n}<\\/pre>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">里面的config配置项，我们放在项目底下的config.php文件中，具体配置内容如下:<\\/p>\\n\\n<pre style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0.6em; padding-bottom: 0.6em; position: relative; overflow: hidden; border-left: 5px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(93, 106, 106); white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; word-break: break-word; letter-spacing: 0.14px;\\\">\\n&nbsp;\\/\\/邮箱设置\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;mail&#39;=&gt;[\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;CharSet&#39;=&gt;&#39;UTF-8&#39;,\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;SMTPDebug&#39;=&gt;0,\\/\\/&nbsp;启用SMTP调试功能&nbsp;0关闭\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;SMTPAuth&#39;=&gt;true,\\/\\/&nbsp;启用&nbsp;SMTP&nbsp;验证功能\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;SMTPSecure&#39;=&gt;&#39;ssl&#39;,\\/\\/&nbsp;安全协议\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;Host&#39;=&gt;&#39;smtp.163.com&#39;,\\/\\/&nbsp;SMTP&nbsp;服务器\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;Port&#39;=&gt;465,\\/\\/&nbsp;SMTP服务器的端口号\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;Username&#39;=&gt;&#39;**********&#39;,\\/\\/&nbsp;SMTP服务器用户名\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;Password&#39;=&gt;&#39;**********&#39;,\\/\\/&nbsp;SMTP服务器密码\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;From&#39;=&gt;&#39;*********@163.com&#39;,\\/\\/&nbsp;发件人邮箱\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;Name&#39;=&gt;&#39;blue&#39;,\\/\\/&nbsp;发件人邮箱\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;]<\\/pre>\\n\\n<h4 style=\\\"margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">2.1<\\/h4>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">这里我们只是实现了smtp协议发送的demo，所以在封装的层面上没有做到很全面，不是很灵活。图中其他两个文件（PhpMailer.php和Smtp.php）是Phpmailer邮件发送类的核心文件，为了简化调用，抽取了出来，详细的用法和参数设置，可以参考gayhub的使用说明<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/PHPMailer\\/PHPMailer\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(36, 121, 204); text-decoration: none;\\\">phpmailer<\\/a><\\/p>\\n\\n<h4 style=\\\"margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">2.2 注意点<\\/h4>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">在此步骤中，我们需要注意几点：1是你设置的邮件发送的账号是否已经开启SMTP并且找对对应的安全协议和端口号。2、当前服务器是否支持SMTP服务，这边很多时候会受一些socket函数的影响，遇到问题的时候，我们应该把SMTPDebug参数设置为1，然后根据debug信息去细心调试。3、发出的邮件有些会被放入垃圾箱，注意查收。<\\/p>\\n\\n<h4 style=\\\"margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">2.3 调用<\\/h4>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">建立如下的文件目录结构：<img alt=\\\"send.png\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/blog.blueyian.top\\/usr\\/uploads\\/2017\\/10\\/2313453912.png\\\" title=\\\"send.png\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">在Index.php中调用发送邮件的方法,具体代码如下<\\/p>\\n\\n<pre style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0.6em; padding-bottom: 0.6em; position: relative; overflow: hidden; border-left: 5px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(93, 106, 106); white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; word-break: break-word; letter-spacing: 0.14px;\\\">\\npublic&nbsp;function&nbsp;sendMail(){\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if(SendMail::postmail(&#39;937069176@qq.com&#39;,&#39;test&#39;,&#39;123&#39;)){\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&#39;send&nbsp;success&#39;;\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}else{\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&#39;send&nbsp;fail&#39;;\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<\\/pre>\\n\\n<h4 style=\\\"margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">2.4 调用结果<\\/h4>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><img alt=\\\"receive.png\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/blog.blueyian.top\\/usr\\/uploads\\/2017\\/10\\/2478100405.png\\\" title=\\\"receive.png\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">我们可以在QQ邮箱的垃圾箱中找到我们刚刚发送的一封邮件<\\/p>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\\"margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 3px 0px 3px 8px; font-size: 1.1em; border-left: 5px solid rgb(60, 140, 221); background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal;\\\">3、结合swoole实现异步群发<\\/h3>\\n\\n<h4 style=\\\"margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">3.1安装swoole<\\/h4>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">swoole扩展安装的详细步骤官网上面都有，不再赘述，<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/wiki.swoole.com\\/wiki\\/page\\/1.html\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(36, 121, 204); text-decoration: none;\\\">swoole文档传送门<\\/a><br \\/>\\n安装完swoole之后，建议为自己的IDE加上swoole的代码提示，<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/github.com\\/eaglewu\\/swoole-ide-helper\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(36, 121, 204); text-decoration: none;\\\">配置IDE提示swoole代码的传送门<\\/a><\\/p>\\n\\n<h4 style=\\\"margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">3.2实现异步群发<\\/h4>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">我们先实现异步的服务端：<\\/p>\\n\\n<pre style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0.6em; padding-bottom: 0.6em; position: relative; overflow: hidden; border-left: 5px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(93, 106, 106); white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; word-break: break-word; letter-spacing: 0.14px;\\\">\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/**\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;description:服务端\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*\\/\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;syncSend(){\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$serv&nbsp;=&nbsp;new&nbsp;\\\\swoole_server(&#39;0.0.0.0&#39;,8082);\\n\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$serv-&gt;set(array(&#39;task_worker_num&#39;&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;4));\\n\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$serv-&gt;on(&#39;receive&#39;,&nbsp;function($serv,&nbsp;$fd,&nbsp;$from_id,&nbsp;$data)&nbsp;{\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$task_id&nbsp;=&nbsp;$serv-&gt;task($data);\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&quot;开始投递异步任务&nbsp;id=$task_id\\\\n&quot;;\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;});\\n\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$serv-&gt;on(&#39;task&#39;,&nbsp;function&nbsp;($serv,&nbsp;$task_id,&nbsp;$from_id,&nbsp;$data)&nbsp;{\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&quot;接收异步任务[id=$task_id]&quot;.PHP_EOL;\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;for&nbsp;($i&nbsp;=&nbsp;0&nbsp;;&nbsp;$i&lt;20;$i++){\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if(SendMail::postmail(&#39;937069176@qq.com&#39;,&#39;test&#39;,$data)){\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&#39;send&#39;.$i.&#39;&nbsp;success&#39;.&quot;\\\\n&quot;;\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}else{\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&#39;send&#39;.$i.&#39;&nbsp;fail&#39;.&quot;\\\\n&quot;;\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$serv-&gt;finish(&#39;&#39;);\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;});\\n\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$serv-&gt;on(&#39;finish&#39;,&nbsp;function&nbsp;($serv,&nbsp;$task_id,&nbsp;$data)&nbsp;{\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&quot;异步任务[id=$task_id]完成&quot;.PHP_EOL;\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;});\\n\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$serv-&gt;start();\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<\\/pre>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">在服务端，我们用了一个20的loop来模拟了群发，实际换成不同的email地址就可。<br \\/>\\n下面我们实现客户端<\\/p>\\n\\n<pre style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0.6em; padding-bottom: 0.6em; position: relative; overflow: hidden; border-left: 5px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(93, 106, 106); white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; word-break: break-word; letter-spacing: 0.14px;\\\">\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\\/**\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;description:客户端\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*\\/\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;function&nbsp;index()\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;{\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$client&nbsp;=&nbsp;new&nbsp;\\\\swoole_client(SWOOLE_SOCK_TCP,&nbsp;SWOOLE_SOCK_SYNC);\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$ret&nbsp;=&nbsp;$client-&gt;connect(&quot;127.0.0.1&quot;,&nbsp;8082);\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if(empty($ret)){\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;echo&nbsp;&#39;error!connect&nbsp;to&nbsp;swoole_server&nbsp;failed&#39;;\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;else&nbsp;{\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$client-&gt;send(&#39;blue&#39;);\\/\\/这里只是简单的实现了发送的内容\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}<\\/pre>\\n\\n<h4 style=\\\"margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">3.3开启服务端<\\/h4>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">这里必须要用CLI方式，我们进入项目的根目录。<br \\/>\\n执行<\\/p>\\n\\n<pre style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0.6em; padding-bottom: 0.6em; position: relative; overflow: hidden; border-left: 5px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(93, 106, 106); white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; word-break: break-word; letter-spacing: 0.14px;\\\">\\nnetstat&nbsp;-apn&nbsp;|&nbsp;grep&nbsp;8082<\\/pre>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">先监测一下8082端口是否被占用，如果占用则<\\/p>\\n\\n<pre style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0.6em; padding-bottom: 0.6em; position: relative; overflow: hidden; border-left: 5px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(93, 106, 106); white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; word-break: break-word; letter-spacing: 0.14px;\\\">\\nkill&nbsp;-9&nbsp;PID(进程号)<\\/pre>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">杀死进程<\\/p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">然后我们执行<\\/p>\\n\\n<pre style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0.6em; padding-bottom: 0.6em; position: relative; overflow: hidden; border-left: 5px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(93, 106, 106); white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; word-break: break-word; letter-spacing: 0.14px;\\\">\\nphp&nbsp;public\\/index.php&nbsp;index\\/index\\/syncSend<\\/pre>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">这条命令的作用是用cli模式来使我们的8082端口处于监听状态。且保持这个终端处于活跃状态，这样方便我们查看发送的结果。<\\/p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">接着我们可以用CLI或者浏览器访问的方式来访问我们的客户端<\\/p>\\n\\n<pre style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0.6em; padding-bottom: 0.6em; position: relative; overflow: hidden; border-left: 5px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(93, 106, 106); white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; word-break: break-word; letter-spacing: 0.14px;\\\">\\nphp&nbsp;public\\/index.php&nbsp;index\\/index\\/index<\\/pre>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">当我们执行一次的时候客户端的时候，我们可以在服务端的终端看到屏幕上面出现如下的画面：<\\/p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><img alt=\\\"sync1.png\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/blog.blueyian.top\\/usr\\/uploads\\/2017\\/10\\/3522049867.png\\\" title=\\\"sync1.png\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">说明我们已经正常群发了。<br \\/>\\n下面，我们就来测试异步，因为163服务器会对IP进行检测，如果在某个时间发送也别频繁的话，会出现发送失败的情况，所以我们测试的时候，采用连续执行4次客户端的方式<br \\/>\\n下面是执行的结果：<\\/p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><img alt=\\\"start.png\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/blog.blueyian.top\\/usr\\/uploads\\/2017\\/10\\/3813820769.png\\\" title=\\\"start.png\\\" \\/><br \\/>\\n<img alt=\\\"end.png\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/blog.blueyian.top\\/usr\\/uploads\\/2017\\/10\\/348279462.png\\\" title=\\\"end.png\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">从图中发送的顺序来看，我们可以很容易的判断，我们已经实现了异步的发送。<br \\/>\\n邮箱里面也接收到了刚刚发送的邮件。<\\/p>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><img alt=\\\"result.png\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/blog.blueyian.top\\/usr\\/uploads\\/2017\\/10\\/4252401539.png\\\" title=\\\"result.png\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\n\\n<h3 style=\\\"margin: 15px 0px 0px; padding: 3px 0px 3px 8px; font-size: 1.1em; border-left: 5px solid rgb(60, 140, 221); background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal;\\\">4、后记~<\\/h3>\\n\\n<p style=\\\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(93, 104, 111); font-family: Lato, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, STHeiti, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">swoole是一种想要熟悉和熟练使用的扩展，但是限于网络编程知识的不足，所以还是要多多测试和学习，demo中有不足的地方，还请指出QAQ<\\/p>\\n\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\n\",\"tags\":\"\",\"category\":\"5\",\"thumb\":\"\\/static\\/upload\\/678855519abe36d4\\/396882c05de6d3a0.jpg\",\"laiyuan\":\"http:\\/\\/blog.blueyian.top\\/index.php\\/archives\\/46\\/\"}', '', '2019-01-06 16:52:17');
