INSERT INTO `system_log` VALUES ('904', '127.0.0.1', 'blog/article/edit', 'admin', 'blog/article/edit', '{\"id\":\"60\",\"title\":\"PECL的安装和使用\",\"isfabu\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p><span style=\\\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">下载并安装pear脚本<\\/span><br \\/>\\n<span style=\\\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">cd \\/usr\\/local\\/php\\/bin\\/<\\/span><br \\/>\\n<span style=\\\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">curl -o go-pear.php http:\\/\\/pear.php.net\\/go-pear.phar<\\/span><br \\/>\\n<br \\/>\\n<br \\/>\\n<span style=\\\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">.\\/php go-pear.php ##回车, 会提示选择安装的东西, 直接回车, 安装全部, 若后面有要选择y\\/n的, 输入y回车<\\/span><br \\/>\\n<br \\/>\\n<br \\/>\\n<span style=\\\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">如果看到下面的一段话就是安装成功:<\\/span><br \\/>\\n<span style=\\\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">Run it without parameters to see the available actions, try&#39;pear list&#39;<\\/span><br \\/>\\n<span style=\\\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">to see what packages are installed, or&#39;pear help&#39;for help.<\\/span><br \\/>\\n<span style=\\\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">For more information about PEAR, see:<\\/span><br \\/>\\n<span style=\\\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">&nbsp; &nbsp; http:\\/\\/pear.php.net\\/faq.php<\\/span><br \\/>\\n<span style=\\\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">&nbsp; &nbsp; http:\\/\\/pear.php.net\\/manual\\/<\\/span><br \\/>\\n<span style=\\\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">Thanks for using go-pear!<\\/span><br \\/>\\n<br \\/>\\n<br \\/>\\n<span style=\\\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">接下来, 就可以直接安装或下载php扩展了<\\/span><br \\/>\\n<span style=\\\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">1.打开网页 http:\\/\\/pecl.php.net\\/packages.php<\\/span><br \\/>\\n<span style=\\\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">2.搜索php扩展<\\/span><br \\/>\\n<span style=\\\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">3.如果存在(Search results (1 - 1 of 1)), 则记下名字, 例如redis<\\/span><br \\/>\\n<span style=\\\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">4.来到linux命令行, 输入: pecl install redis 或 pecl download redis<\\/span><br \\/>\\n<span style=\\\"color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, SimHei, Arial, SimSun; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">有时候可能install会失败, 那就只能download源码包到本地自己动手进行编译安装了<\\/span><\\/p>\\n\",\"tags\":\"\",\"category\":\"5\",\"thumb\":\"\\/static\\/upload\\/2b29212d1a3ea182\\/d3743f34aa9c94e9.jpg\",\"laiyuan\":\"\"}', '', '2019-01-06 16:53:14');
